I have one tip to add:<br>
<br>
When dropping rods, use the <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> /fastdrop on</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> command to turn the drop confirmation box off.  You can quickly re-enable it after you've finished by typing <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> /fastdrop off</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
