<br>
3 in regen AND 3 in bind. how does that affect self mana regen?<br>
<br>
Protection of the Cabbage buff. This buff totally rocks and if your 59+ druids dont have it make them spend 1k to do the short version of the quest and get it!!!<br>
<br>
Protection of the Cabbage<br>
1: Increase Armor Class (AC) by 24 (L59)<br>
2: Increase Total Hit Points from 467 (L59) to 470 (L60)<br>
3: Increase Current Hitpoints from 467 (L59) to 470 (L60)<br>
4: Regeneration for 6000 Mana in 1000 ticks<br>
<br>
Classes: Dru (L59)<br>
<br>
Mana Cost: 500<br>
Spell Duration: 1000 ticks (100.0 minutes)<br>
<br>
From what I hear this stacks with TPP. No HP regen but a very nice mana regen component. Like a lower level PotG that is self targeted.<br>
